    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various, usually copper or aluminum, coins issued since the late 18th century by several French-speaking countries and valued at one-hundredth part of their monetary unit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
